casebody.data:
In re RYALLS. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. March 1, 1894.) Accounting by Sarah M. Ryalls, as administratrix of William H. Ryalls, deceased, who was executor of Elizabeth Haney, deceased.

Argued before MAYHAM, P. X, and HERRICK and PUTNAM, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for rcargument granted. See 26 N. Y. Supp. 815.
